TESTIMONIAL_SECTION_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER: Trusted by developers and projects across the Ethereum ecosystem.
TESTIMONIAL_1_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: InsightEth provides invaluable real-time analytics for monitoring new Ethereum transactions. Their platform helps us quickly identify and investigate any anomalies.
TESTIMONIAL_2_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: The InsightEth team's expertise in blockchain data has been instrumental in optimizing our smart contract monitoring process. Their transaction insights are game-changing.
TESTIMONIAL_3_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: InsightEth's transaction analysis tools give us a comprehensive view of user activity across our dApps. Their platform is a must-have for any Ethereum project.
FEATURE_1_BODY: Stay ahead of the game with our advanced Ethereum transaction monitoring and analysis tools. Get instant alerts and insights on new transactions as they happen.
FEATURE_2_BODY: Dive deep into the details of each transaction with comprehensive data covering gas prices, contract interactions, token transfers, and more.
FEATURE_3_BODY: Keep tabs on smart contract activity by tracking function calls, state changes, and events emitted on the Ethereum blockchain.
FEATURE_4_BODY: Set up custom alerts to notify you of transactions matching specific criteria, such as high-value transfers or interactions with specific contracts.
FEATURE_5_BODY: Seamlessly integrate on-chain data into your applications and workflows, enabling powerful analysis and decision-making capabilities.
FEATURE_6_BODY: Leverage our robust APIs to build custom solutions tailored to your needs, ensuring smooth integration with your existing tech stack.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: This app allows you to analyze new Ethereum transactions in real-time as they occur on the blockchain. It provides insights into transaction details, sender/receiver addresses, amount transferred, and more.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: The app connects to Ethereum nodes and listens for new transaction events. When a new transaction is detected, it is parsed and analyzed, with relevant details displayed in an easy-to-understand format.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Stay up-to-date on the latest Ethereum activity, monitor transactions of interest, detect suspicious transactions, and gain valuable insights into network usage and trends.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, this transaction analysis app is completely free to use. However, premium features like advanced filtering and notifications may require a paid subscription.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our Ethereum transaction analysis app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides real-time analysis of new transactions on the Ethereum blockchain. It monitors the network, detects new transactions, and analyzes them for insights like value transferred, contract interactions, and more.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We run Ethereum nodes that listen for new blocks and transactions. When a new transaction occurs, our app decodes it, follows internal calls, and extracts relevant data to provide a detailed analysis.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: You can see the value transferred, any ERC20 token transfers, contract deployments, internal contract calls, failed transactions, and more. We also identify transactions from major DeFi protocols.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Our analysis happens in real-time, within seconds of a new transaction being broadcasted to the Ethereum network. You get insights as soon as transactions occur.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, in addition to real-time monitoring, we also have parsed data going back years that you can query and analyze using our API or data export tools.
